TextEng: Goodbye.
Is this the Golem Emporium on Northwest Vizier Street?
What do you know about the mythal?
What frightens you about the mythal's return?
Why did the mythal abandon you?
Why are you excited about the mythal's return?
What is the mythal capable of?
The mythallar? What are those?
The Temple of the Winds?
Who... What are you?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Customers? What did people come here to buy?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 손님? 사람들이 여기서 뭘 사러 왔는데?

TextEng: These guardians... I need to destroy them. Tell me how.
Text: 그 수호자들을... 파괴해야 해. 방법을 알려줘.

TextEng: How did he keep them gentle?
Where is this ring?
But I must! I need that ring.
Text: 안 되지만 어쩔 수 없어! 그 반지가 필요하다고.

TextEng: You loved your maker?
Forgive me, your speech is hard to follow.
Text: 미안한데, 네 말이 잘 안 들려.

TextEng: I hunt a medusa named Heurodis.
Back to my other questions.
She planned to study the city's lore and wisdom.
She hoped to study the magic of ancient Netheril.
She came to plunder the treasures of Undrentide.
She wanted to rule the city, make it fly again.
Text: 도시를 지배하고 다시 날게 만들려고 왔대.

TextEng: What can you tell me about the rest of the city?
Text: 도시의 다른 구역에 대해 말해 줘.

TextEng: What lay at the city's center?
What lay to the west?
What lay to the south?
What lay to the east?
What lay to the north?
There must be a way in!
What great buildings?
